Bio

Frazier Baker is a machine learning researcher. He is currently pursuing his PhD at The Ohio State University, advised by Dr. Xia Ning. He has previously worked as a Research Scientist in Georgia Tech Research Institute's Advanced Concepts Laboratory. Frazier received his Masters of Science in Computer Science from the University of Cincinnati in December 2019, advised by Dr. Aleksey Porollo. He received his Bachelor of Science in Computer Science in May 2019 from the University of Cincinnati.
